{"title":"举杯（外一首）","authors":["汪国真"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":3,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"举杯（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪国真"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们为相遇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起晶莹的酒杯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知过去的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实就是这次邂逅的准备"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜，张开黑色的帷幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月，洒下温柔的清辉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾袅袅  风微微"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌进心头的是潮水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溢出眼眶的是眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天，我们各自"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形影相吊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山路上彷徨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，我们手携着手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在星光下与清风共醉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生呵！有多少痛苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会有多少欢乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你多少磨砺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会给你多少珠贝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月流去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流不去的是一身锋芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是昆仑凝雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是南海波光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依稀中原逐鹿古战场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把杯举起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把月挂起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把剑舞起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌一阕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一舞剑器动四方”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿人生如剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立起——寒光四射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躺倒——四射寒光"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}